snippet.title: Life is Feudal: MMO trailer
snippet.description:
Use a sword to carve your way to glory, or achieve universal recognition through a peaceful craft. In LiF: MMO, only you decide what your path will be. Fight and seize lands, build impregnable castles and fortresses, master trade and peaceful crafts. Get ready for an epic journey through the harsh and dangerous lands of the medieval world!

Learn more:
https://www.lifeisfeudalmmo.com

Join our Discord server to stay tuned:
https://discord.gg/QDrMBsvGMg

Join us on social media:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/LiF.MMO/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/lifeisfeudalmmo
